{
  "stem": "5883.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I been working all the time till 1943. 1943 was, I think, it was-- it would be September, when they came the last time with a-- a lot of trucks to the ghetto to get everybody else away already.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by that time, everybody got smart already and made themselves some hideouts in the house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But where we lived, we made a hideout under the steps going to the basement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we woke up that morning, and we saw all those trucks, we were-- you know, they could figure-- my father and mother figured out that something be not right, and we climbed into that hideout.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, we didn't have any food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing in there because we never knew when they will come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you couldn't get ready for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, they started chasing everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could hear the soldiers walking in the house, looking probably for people, and chasing everybody out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it got quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it looks like everybody was gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we sat there for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the third day-- there was a main water pipe in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The water pipe busted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had no choice but leave, because the water started coming up-- up to our necks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we waited till the evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we came out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went into the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the dark, we changed our clothes, because we couldn't make anything, you know, lights, because you didn't know who's walking around outside.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother had prepared us a place we had to hide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Across from the ghetto, there lived Christian people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one of those people, my mother, you know, gave them money, gave them whatever we had so they will hide us out.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
